OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain at first,
OL,6,Fclearing northeast in the morning to
OL,7,Fallow some bright spells. A band of
OL,8,Frain will pass through in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with strengthening south to
OL,10,Fsouthwest winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain soon clearing Shetland
OL,13,Fin the evening. Otherwise clear spells
OL,14,Fand scattered blustery showers, heavy
OL,15,Fat times. Strong southwest winds,
OL,16,Fcoastal gales possible later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
