OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers in the morning, showers
OL,7,Fbecoming less frequent in the
OL,8,Fafternoon allowing longer sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Strong southwest winds at
OL,10,Ffirst, veering westerly and easing in
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,14,Fdry with bright spells on Saturday,
OL,15,Fthe odd shower possible. Stronger
OL,16,Fsoutherly winds on Sunday and Monday
OL,17,Fwith variable cloud and occasional
OL,18,Foutbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
